				<content translate="true">Early Literacy</content>
			</text>
			<text id="text" x="225" y="40" width="331" height="" autosize="H" style="PANEL" visible="true" fx="">
				<content translate="true">&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;Literacy development begins in the very early stages of childhood. &lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;Research shows that both the relationship with parents and caregivers, and the quality of the child's literacy environment, play a significant role in determining his or her preparedness for and early success in school. &lt;/P&gt;</content>
			</text>
