				<content translate="true">Early Literacy Activities</content>
			</text>
			<text id="text" x="225" y="40" width="340" height="" autosize="H" style="PANEL" visible="true" fx="">
				<content translate="true">&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;Often the activities of young children may not seem related to reading and writing. &lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;Early behaviors such as “reading” from pictures and “writing” with scribbles are examples of emergent literacy and are an important part of a child’s &lt;/P&gt;&lt;P ALIGN="LEFT"&gt;literacy development. &lt;/P&gt;</content>
			</text>
		</container>
